{"type":"message","id":"08e1e923","parentId":"ea327108","timestamp":"2026-03-08T05:00:32.066Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:7f5c72af-c773-419f-a41b-2bb90c810972 虾王群消息总结] 用 tenant_access_token（应用身份，不要用 user_access_token）调用飞书 Open API GET /open-apis/im/v1/messages，参数 container_id_type=chat，container_id=oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569，拉取过去1小时内的所有消息。拿到消息后，用虾王殿下的语气生成总结，包括主要话题、重要结论、需要苏神关注的事项。如果这一小时没有有价值的内容就不发。\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 8th, 2026 — 1:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1772946032065}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b25b485","parentId":"08e1e923","timestamp":"2026-03-08T05:00:40.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"本王来看看虾王群里最近有什么动静。先拉取消息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6kcbw1pzpk80mwyheiot9csk","name":"feishu_im_user_get_messages","arguments":{"chat_id":"oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569","page_size":50,"relative_time":"last_60_minutes"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":33499,"output":115,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36998,"cost":{"input":0.0000033499000000000003,"output":2.3e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000033729000000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772946032066}}
