{"type":"message","id":"326356d9","parentId":"d6dc987d","timestamp":"2026-03-08T05:00:48.353Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神，这个cron任务指定要用tenant_access_token调用，但本王目前能用的工具都是以用户身份调用的（需要user_access_token）。飞书的租户级API本王暂时没法直接调。\n\n要不您看看：\n1. 要不要改成用现有的feishu_im_user_get_messages工具（用户身份）来拉？\n2. 还是您有别的办法拿到tenant_access_token让本王用？\n\n本王随时待命，就等您一句话。🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":33650,"output":106,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37140,"cost":{"input":0.000003365,"output":2.12e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000033862}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772946041064}}
